你对外讲的时候，最漂亮的版本

你可以这样说：

We should not frame this as a broad substitution question between Home Health and SNF.
The higher-value question is where members fall out of the expected SNF recovery pathway, what happens afterward, and which of those gaps represent an opportunity for targeted home-based support.

这句非常像高层会喜欢的 framing。

